{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for bullet list component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomBulletListComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the bullet list component tokens you want.","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSmall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomBulletListComponentTokensProvider: BulletListComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomBulletListComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(bulletList: CustomBulletListComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(bulletList: CustomBulletListComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let bulletListComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let bulletListComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider(","                                                spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B38ThemeBulletListComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bullet list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bullet list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBulletList"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBulletListComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BulletListComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bullet list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/init(spaces:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{